high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink
Pick up the sponge in the sink
Turn and face the plate that is in the sink
Put the sponge on the plate that is in the sink
Pick up the plate and sponge in the sink
Turn left and move towards the cabinets on the right
Open the cabinet, place the plate inside and close the cabinets
anns.task_desc: Place the sponge on the plate and move them to the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the sponge out of the sink.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the sponge on the black plate that is in the sink.
Pick up the black plate with the sponge on it.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet and put the plate with the sponge on it inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a sponge on it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn complete around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the sponge from the sink.
Step to the right and face the sink.
Put the sponge on the plate that is in the sink.
Pick up the plate and sponge from the sink.
Turn left and walk forward to the wall. Turn right to face the counter. Look up at the cabinets above the counter.
Place the plate and sponge inside the cabinet. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge and plate away in a cabinet.
